# .aiignore
#
# AI Ignore File - Project-Specific AI Rules and Configurations
# Similar to .gitignore but for AI/Claude Code configurations
#
# Files and directories listed here will NEVER be synced to the boilerplate
# or shared with other projects. They are PROJECT-SPECIFIC ONLY.
#
# Usage: When you say "this is for this project only" or "don't sync this",
# those rules/files get added here.
#
# Examples of what belongs in .aiignore:
# - Project-specific business rules
# - Client-specific requirements
# - Custom agents for this project only
# - Sensitive project context
# - Domain-specific configurations
#

# ============================================================================
# PROJECT-SPECIFIC CONFIGURATIONS (Never sync these)
# ============================================================================

# Project-specific rules and context
.claude/project-specific/
.claude/local/
.claude/custom/

# Project-only agents (custom to this project)
.claude/agents/project-*.md
.claude/agents/local-*.md

# Project-only documentation
.claude/docs/project-specific/
.claude/docs/client/
.claude/docs/business-rules/

# Project-specific personas
.claude/personas/project-*.md

# Local AI configuration overrides
.claude/local-config.json
.claude/project-overrides.json

